    <Statements>
      <Statement>(+) Know and apply the Binomial Theorem for the expansion of (&lt;i&gt;x&lt;/i&gt; + &lt;i&gt;y&lt;/i&gt;)&lt;sup&gt;&lt;i&gt;n&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; in powers of &lt;i&gt;x&lt;/i&gt; and &lt;i&gt;y&lt;/i&gt; for a positive integer &lt;i&gt;n&lt;/i&gt;, where &lt;i&gt;x&lt;/i&gt; and &lt;i&gt;y&lt;/i&gt; are any numbers, with coefficients determined for example by Pascal&amp;rsquo;s Triangle.&lt;sup&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt;</Statement>
